
# The Flying Bus - Environment Variables Example
# 
# This project uses Supabase for backend services and secrets management.
# No .env file is required - all configuration is handled through Supabase.
#
# To set up the project:
# 1. Connect to Supabase via the green button in Lovable
# 2. Add secrets through Supabase dashboard: Project > Settings > Edge Functions
# 3. Use the lov-secret-form action in Lovable chat to add secrets securely
#
